videos.description: Jamal Morrow finds a seam in the defense and gets into the open field to rip off a 30-yard run.
videos.headline: Morrow bursts out of the backfield for big Cougars gain

videos.description: Luke Falk evades pressure in the pocket and rolls right before throwing deep the end zone where the ball goes off the hands of Jamire Calvin, forcing Washington State to kick a field goal.
videos.headline: Falk's third-and-10 heave dropped in end zone

videos.description: Erik Powell hits a 44-yard field goal to give the Cougars a 3-0 lead over the Trojans.
videos.headline: Washington State finishes opening drive with field goal

videos.description: Sam Darnold scrambles for an easy 4-yard touchdown on USC's first drive of the game against Washington State.
videos.headline: Darnold rushes in for TD

videos.description: Luke Falk throws it deep to Renard Bell who is past the USC defense for a long gain into Trojan territory.
videos.headline: Falk airs it out for 61-yard gain

videos.description: Luke Falk tosses a screen pass to Tavares Martin Jr. who runs downfield for a 28-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Washington State scores on screen pass

videos.description: Washington State's Sean Harper Jr. jumps the route and intercepts Sam Darnold's pass in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Cougar defender reads Darnold for INT

videos.description: Ronald Jones II runs away from the Cougars' defense for a long touchdown to give USC the lead back.
videos.headline: Jones II shows off speed for 86-yard TD

videos.description: Uchenna Nwosa jumps in front of Luke Falk's pass and intercepts it, giving the Trojans the ball on the Washington State 3-yard line, which would lead to a field goal.
videos.headline: USC picks off Falk deep in Cougar territory

videos.description: Jamal Morrow makes a great cut at the line of scrimmage and walks into the end zone for a 1-yard touchdown late in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Morrow cuts into end zone to tie game

videos.description: Washington State coach Mike Leach says his team played more "characteristic" in the second quarter after falling behind early, and says his squad is a second-half team.
videos.headline: Leach pleased with how Cougars closed out half

videos.description: Both USC and Washington State hit on big plays in the first half, but Jamal Morrow's 1-yard touchdown run in the final seconds tied the game at 17-17.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Late TD draws Cougars even with Trojans) 2017/09/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Late TD draws Cougars even with Trojans

videos.description: On third-and-14, Luke Falk stands tall in the pocket and takes a huge hit and gets the ball away to get the first down.
videos.headline: Falk takes huge hit, still converts on third down

videos.description: Midway through the second quarter, Luke Falk completes a pass to give him 1,188 for his college career, the most in conference history.
videos.headline: Falk sets Pac-12 record for completions

videos.description: Luke Falk throws a short pass to Jamal Morrow and Morrow does the rest to score a 23-yard touchdown. It's the 105th TD pass of Falk's career, tying him with Marcus Mariota for the second most in Pac-12 history.
videos.headline: Morrow scampers to pay dirt

videos.description: With USC staying on the field on a long fourth down, Sam Darnold throws a jump ball to Tyler Vaughns to keep the drive going.
videos.headline: USC converts on fourth-and-13

videos.description: Sam Darnold caps off a huge drive for the Trojans with a 2-yard TD run to the end zone.
videos.headline: Darnold's second rushing TD ties game

videos.description: Jamal Morrow bursts into the second level and gets all the way down to the USC 23-yard line for a big gain of 35 yards.
videos.headline: Morrow breaks free into Trojans territory

videos.description: Erik Powell hits a 32-yard field goal to give Washington State a 30-27 lead over USC with under two minutes to play in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Cougars take lead on late field goal

videos.description: Sam Darnold gets hit by Jahad Woods and loses the ball. Nate DeRider recovers the ball for the Cougars.
videos.headline: Darnold's fumble seals Washington State win

videos.description: Washington State QB Luke Falk reacts to the Cougars' big 30-27 victory over #5 USC.
videos.headline: Falk: Win over USC is 'stepping stone'

videos.description: After No. 16 Washington State edges No. 5 USC 30-27, the Cougars' fans jump onto to the field to celebrate with the team.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Fans storm the field after Cougars top Trojans) 2017/09/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Fans storm the field after Cougars top Trojans

videos.description: Adam Amin and Dusty Dvoracek break down No. 16 Washington State's upset win over No. 5 USC.
videos.headline: Dvoracek: 'Biggest win of Mike Leach era'

videos.description: Washington State coach Mike Leach expresses how happy he is with his team's 30-27 win over USC and what this means for the program moving forward.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Interview (Leach proud of his team after upset win over USC) 2017/09/29 SC

videos.headline: Leach proud of his team after upset win over USC

videos.description: Desmond Howard notes that Sam Darnold has turned into a turnover machine and USC has suffered a lot of injuries, which will make it difficult for the Trojans to recover.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Analysis (Howard says USC is spiraling out of control) 2017/09/30 CGD

videos.headline: Howard says USC is spiraling out of control
